I've had food at this place everytime I've been to Goa and it has always been very good. Thei lentil soup, squid masala fry, fillet of fish is a must try. Servis staff super friendly!!
Food: 5/5  |  Service: 5/5  |  Atmosphere: 5/5
Group of १०
Recommended dishes
Prawn Curry, Prawns Masala Fry, lentil soup, cheese chilly garlic nan..

Lovely place in Arpora to chill out and eat from a selection of varied cuisines. We had a perfectly cooked Tandoori chicken and a delightful Carbonara. Ended the meal with a Serradora (goan dessert) which could have been better, but no complaints!! A definite recommend amongst the hoardes of restaurants that have sprung up of late.

Absolutely fantastic evening!
The food at You & me was incredible. We had  few dishes and everything was cooked to perfection with amazing flavors. The service was top-notch – our server was attentive, friendly, and made sure we had everything we needed.
The bar had a great selection of drinks, and we enjoyed. The live music was the perfect touch – the boy (Rudraksh_music) was incredibly talented and created such a lively atmosphere.
We had an unforgettable time and will definitely be back soon! Highly recommend.
